    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这款屡获殊荣的黑色喜剧游戏以令人手忙脚乱的电视直播为题材，被评论家称为“<i>奇异的杰作</i>”和“<i>很可能是史上最佳的全动态影像游戏</i>”，如今也可以在虚拟现实中游玩了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0ef05fd58abb45b6a5628852372ef562.poster.avif?t=1752165936\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0ef05fd58abb45b6a5628852372ef562.webm?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0ef05fd58abb45b6a5628852372ef562.mp4?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《不予播出》虚拟现实版采用了原版获奖全动态影像冒险游戏的游戏玩法、故事情节和扣人心弦的黑色喜剧风格，可让你比以往更接近新闻行业。全面了解整个新闻编辑室，与你的设备进行互动，克服一切困难，勇敢地追寻真相。<br><br>我们保证提供身临其境的游戏体验，你会感觉自己<i>真的因为维护不善的设备触电了</i>！<br><br>趾高气扬的名人、道貌岸然的政客和莫名其妙的赞助商在电视播出期间引发各种冲突。而你要负责确保节目在任何情况下都顺利播出。或者说，你赚的就是这份辛苦钱。现在大概没什么能阻止你整天用录像带砸自己的头了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亲手挑选头条新闻！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0da023092b2a4e1a3b53938d379c56ad.poster.avif?t=1752165936\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0da023092b2a4e1a3b53938d379c56ad.webm?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/0da023092b2a4e1a3b53938d379c56ad.mp4?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过神奇的虚拟现实，领略如今已不复存在的录像带播放体验。小心地摆放“空调”，以免你的办公室在播放新闻时温度过高，在广告期间又电扇狂转（不过要注意电缆）。<br><br>另外，你可以对任何你不赞同的政治意识形态愤怒地挥舞拳头（或者对人也行，没关系，他们看不到你）。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为画面定调；为辩论定调</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/3fb3a9c7849f4d774e12ef556a090b97.poster.avif?t=1752165936\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/3fb3a9c7849f4d774e12ef556a090b97.webm?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/3fb3a9c7849f4d774e12ef556a090b97.mp4?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>运用编辑技巧让公众感到愉悦，并密切关注收视率。让政治家看起来贪婪或勇敢，让抵抗组织的领袖看起来高尚或暴力，让新闻主播看起来迷人或精神错乱。你决定在屏幕上展现的人物和内容可能会改变历史进程。不要有负担哦。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >确保节目适合儿童观看</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/383a25596c762cd673b3c70c5137af43.poster.avif?t=1752165936\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/383a25596c762cd673b3c70c5137af43.webm?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257770/extras/383a25596c762cd673b3c70c5137af43.mp4?t=1752165936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>虚拟现实版正是为了模拟按下那些看起来很重要的红色按钮而诞生的。猛砸那些红色按钮（或者轻敲；两种方式都可以），以避免粗鲁言语（和其他敏感信息）播出。确保新闻内容对儿童和专制政权而言都适宜观看。<br><br>坐在地板上，不理会各种混乱，加载广告，调高音量，让自己沉浸在整个国家的梦想、恐惧、希望和神经质中。",
